description: Palladium One Mining Inc. explores for and develops mineral resource properties. The company primarily explores for palladium, platinum, gold, copper, cobalt, and nickel. Its flagship property is its 100% interest in the Lantinen Koillismaa project located in north-central Finland. Palladium One Mining Inc. is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Derrick H. Weyrauch C.A., CPA, CA, CPA
